    'In order to perform any ride sharing or rental activity on our Platform, you will need to provide an SMS verified mobile phone number. This is a way to authenticate your identity and create a trusted environment for other users. The processing of mobile phone information is based on KnockKnocks legitimate interest in ensuring a trusted environment for all users (Article 6 (1 ) (f) of GDPR) and is necessary for the performance of the contract with you (article 6 (1) (b) of GDPR).'=>'Para realizar cualquier actividad de transporte compartido o alquiler en
