    'Your user data will be keep while your account is active, as they are necessary to complete the us s public profile, are used to facilitate a booking transaction or are necessary for the purposes risk and insurance. When you close your account, we will delete your user data six months after the closure of the account, to unless you have outstanding payments or we have considered necessary to keep your data for reasons related to risks, insurance or criminal investigations. The messages that you send to another user on the platform will be kept as long as your account is active. Messages will be retained for a period of 6 months after the closure of the account. This is for ensure that we still have the ability to help with any complaints, insurance cases, or criminal investigations related to a previous reservation. If you want to remove specific information shared with another user before the deletion period ends, contact us by email with a request in which specify what information you want to remove. We will remove the information as soon as possible, and in any case not more than 30 days after receipt of a valid application by written. We reserve the right to refuse removal if the removal request is related to a claim active or potential customer, insurance case, or criminal investigation. Contact details are in the section 7 ("Contact").'=>'Tus datos de usuario se
